  "text": "STRUCT-FAITHFULNESS is a structured version of FAITHFULNESS, replacing x and y with their natural classes N β (x) and N β (y) where β indexes types of classes, ranging over {manner, place, phonation, isOral, isCentral, height, backness, roundedness}. This feature set is reminiscent of the featurized representation of [CITATION_1] .",
